args: Wait, am I getting mushy? Is this mush?\nWhat's even HAPPENING to me right now?

Augh! I've never felt like this before!
I just wanna pick her up and give her
big squishy hugs and pets on her
little squishy head!
Nya? Is that fresh meat I smell?!
Aww, she's even adorable when she's\nrunning away from me very, very quickly!
But WHY am I so hung up on this Felyne?
My goal has always been to seek out\npowerful warriors in the hopes of one\nday knowing what defeat is like.
That stayed the case even after Elisanne\nhanded me my very first loss.
Focus, Vanessa... Focus on losing...\nFocus on the thrill of combat...
Aaaaugh! I can't do it! My stupid brain is\ncrammed full of thoughts about kitty!
Oh kiiiitty... I wanna be with yoooou...\nWanna pet your fur and do do de dooo...

The Felyne in question is a Lynian from another
world. The human, Vanessa, has been utterly
entranced by her, and now spends her days
creeping about in pursuit of the furry creature.
Nya! What's a banana peel doing here?!
Oh no, kitty! I should go help her!\n...Er, but what do I say?
Whew! I was in trouble there\nfor a second...
Hrmm... That bookshelf is just\nout of my reach...
Right! This time, I'll help her for sure!\n...Gah! Too...nervous! Feet...won't move!
You trying to reach this book?\nHere you go.
Mrow? Oh, I'm very curious about this.
Okay, this time I'll do it for SURE!\nCome on, body! Move! Move your\nstupid joints and...just...go...over...
Yes, you are VERY curious indeed, nya.
*pant* *heave* *wheeze* S-sorry, kitty.\nMy heart started pounding like nobody's\nbusiness there for a second.
Is it paw-sible you're sick or\nsomething, nya?
Sick? I dunno. Maybe? I guess I could be?\nBasically, my heart starts doing the tango\nwhenever I look at you.
It's like I want to be with you all the time.\nIt's a feeling and it's WEIRD!
Sure. You want me to be your Palico\nand go on hunts with you.
Makes sense. You've gotten comfortable\nwith your Kirin gear, so nyow all that's left\nis furr you to get a Palico.
And while I'm honored that you'd tap me\nfor the position...there's a purr-oblem.
See, I already have a meowster, and it's\nbad form for a Palico to try and work with\ntwo different hunters.
But I'd be happy to help you out with stuff\nOTHER than that! You just meow the word,\nI'll do it! ...Er, if I can, that is.
(Anything?! ANYTHING?!\nOh geez, what do I ask for?!)

(I'm not looking to test my strength
against her, and I hadn't even thought
about Palicoes... Oh, no! I haven't thought
about what I really want to do at all!)
(Think, Vanessa. THINK! What should\nyou do with kitty? What? Whaaaaat?!)
I want you to be with me!
Maybe I wasn't 100 purr-cent clear.\nI already have someone.
Yeah, I know. Which is why I don't want\nyou to be my Palico or whatever it is.\nI just want you to be my...friend.
I've never had someone just want to be\nfur-iends before—and especially not\nsomeone who's so EARNEST about it!
This is new, but...sure! Why not?\nLet's be fur-iends.
But yay! Yay for us, kitty! We're gonna\nbe the bestest friends EVER!
